ActFederal Courts Act
SubjectRules Amending the Federal Courts Rules
PrecisRules Amending the FEDERAL COURTS RULES in order to (1) provide greater clarity to the Rules by eliminating contradictions between the English and French versions and by eliminating inconsistencies between different rules; and (2) reduce duplication by limiting the number of paper copies to be filed in certain instances.
